# sqlite-amalgamation.version — pinned sqlite3 amalgamation build number.
#
# Shared by build-macos.sh (darwin-arm64) and linux-bundle.Dockerfile.
# Format: sqlite3 version as a single integer (e.g. 3460000 = 3.46.0).
# See https://www.sqlite.org/download.html for current versions.
#
# To update: change this number, update the download URL year if needed,
# and test both macOS and Linux builds.
3460000
